{"type": "article", "id": 4456, "title": "Nuna Popsicles 冰棒", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-17T08:04:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052331506QuoS1hpTRm479IH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自德国柏林的冰棒品牌 Nuna 日前推出了一款自称是“世界上最美味”的冰棒 Nuna Popsicles 。敢提出这样的口号，Nuna 的底气来自于其跨领域的研发团队，据悉，Nuna Popsicles 别致的几何造型出自于建筑师 Manu Kumar 和设计师 Stefan Gandl 之手，而最关键的口味则请来了国际知名厨师 Heiko Antoniewicz 操刀，采用天然有机成分，制成了这款透出渐变色系效果的立体冰棒。此外，这款冰棒的竹棍也是可以回收利用的。目前，Nuna Popsicles 还未正式上市。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233148LYGPgZ5Vp1C68beF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523314863y5SMHerlTKc1nY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233149fciIxzQMoP6A4dsK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.01875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052331494SEkzHaj5UuC2xRe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}